Hilltop was first listed as a CDP in the [[2000 United States census|2000 U.S. census]].<ref name="2000CensusP004" /><ref name="1990CensusGA" /> As of the [[census]] of 2000, there were 401 people, 119 households, and 91 families residing in the CDP.<ref name="GR2" /> By the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 245 people in the CDP.

